H0.text: What is the anatomical name for the upper jaw bone. Mandibula

H1.text: What is the anatomical name for the upper jaw bone. Zygoma

H2.text: What is the anatomical name for the upper jaw bone. Lacrimal

H3.text: What is the anatomical name for the upper jaw bone. Maxilla

A4.text: The mandible is the movable part of the jaw.

A5.text: The maxilla is the upper fixed bone of the jaw formed from the fusion of two maxillary bones.
